375
00:20:54,259 --> 00:20:56,460
[SPEAKER_00] To je ovako razmišljanje

376
00:20:56,460 --> 00:20:59,859
[SPEAKER_00] Koje se pokušava nadovezati na Bibliju

377
00:20:59,859 --> 00:21:01,319
[SPEAKER_00] I razumijeti što se dogodilo

378
00:21:01,319 --> 00:21:04,339
[SPEAKER_00] Adam i Eva su bili bića od svjetla

379
00:21:04,339 --> 00:21:06,539
[SPEAKER_00] Svjetlo im je bilo zaštita

380
00:21:06,539 --> 00:21:08,480
[SPEAKER_00] U svjetlu su imali odjeću

381
00:21:08,480 --> 00:21:10,000
[SPEAKER_00] Nisu imali druge odjeće

382
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:11,559
[SPEAKER_00] Nego su imali svjetlo

383
00:21:11,559 --> 00:21:13,460
[SPEAKER_00] I tako su se susretali s Bogom

384
00:21:13,460 --> 00:21:16,240
[SPEAKER_00] Biblija kaže da bi Bog dolazio poslije podne

385
00:21:16,240 --> 00:21:18,500
[SPEAKER_00] Šetao, oni bi se susretali s njime

386
00:21:18,500 --> 00:21:19,819
[SPEAKER_00] I što je učinio grijeh?

387
00:21:19,819 --> 00:21:23,599
[SPEAKER_00] Rastrgao im odjeću od svjetla

388
00:21:23,599 --> 00:21:25,599
[SPEAKER_00] I ostali su goli

389
00:21:25,599 --> 00:21:28,619
[SPEAKER_00] I tad su se vidjeli goli

390
00:21:28,619 --> 00:21:36,380
[SPEAKER_00] I su izgubili sjaj svetosti, sjaj netaknutosti, sjaj Božje blizine

391
00:21:36,380 --> 00:21:38,579
[SPEAKER_00] To svjetlo u kojem su bili obučeni

392
00:21:38,579 --> 00:21:41,160
[SPEAKER_00] Raspršilo se, nestalo

393
00:21:41,160 --> 00:21:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] I oni su vidjeli

394
00:21:41,920 --> 00:21:43,160
[SPEAKER_00] Koli

395
00:21:43,160 --> 00:21:46,420
[SPEAKER_00] I što je Bog napravio?

396
00:21:46,420 --> 00:21:51,460
[SPEAKER_00] Kad ih je izvodio iz vrta u kojoj više nema povratka

397
00:21:51,460 --> 00:21:55,460
[SPEAKER_00] Kaže Biblija da im je napravio odjeću od kože

398
00:21:55,460 --> 00:21:57,900
[SPEAKER_00] Koje kože

399
00:21:57,900 --> 00:22:00,440
[SPEAKER_00] Kažu neki teolozi

400
00:22:00,440 --> 00:22:02,099
[SPEAKER_00] To je ta koža

401
00:22:02,099 --> 00:22:04,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ova tu, ne neka druga

402
00:22:04,619 --> 00:22:05,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ova tu

403
00:22:05,900 --> 00:22:08,619
[SPEAKER_00] Naša ljudska koža

404
00:22:08,619 --> 00:22:10,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ona nas štiti

405
00:22:10,599 --> 00:22:14,480
[SPEAKER_00] Da ne budemo tako osjetljivi, tako ranjivi

406
00:22:14,480 --> 00:22:16,000
[SPEAKER_00] To je slika za sljedeće

407
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:19,140
[SPEAKER_00] Kada smo mi skinuli kožu sa sebe

408
00:22:19,140 --> 00:22:22,359
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo bili jako osjetljivi

409
00:22:22,359 --> 00:22:26,619
[SPEAKER_00] To otprilike znači čovjek bez grijeha

410
00:22:26,619 --> 00:22:30,640
[SPEAKER_00] Otvoren Bogu je silno osjetljiv

411
00:22:30,640 --> 00:22:31,579
[SPEAKER_00] Za sve

412
00:22:31,579 --> 00:22:34,859
[SPEAKER_00] Za dodir, za dobrotu, za svjetlo

413
00:22:34,859 --> 00:22:39,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nas je grijeh učinio ranjivima

414
00:22:39,539 --> 00:22:42,279
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ta osjetljivost je samo rana

415
00:22:42,279 --> 00:22:44,880
[SPEAKER_00] A ne više osjetljivost života

416
00:22:44,880 --> 00:22:48,420
[SPEAKER_00] Pa nas je Bog zaštiti od toga da ne trpimo

417
00:22:48,420 --> 00:22:51,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ali kažem to nije biblijski

418
00:22:51,019 --> 00:22:52,740
[SPEAKER_00] To ostavite po strani

419
00:22:52,740 --> 00:22:54,779
[SPEAKER_00] To je samo da razumijemo

420
00:22:54,779 --> 00:22:56,599
[SPEAKER_00] Kako ova slika

421
00:22:56,599 --> 00:22:58,180
[SPEAKER_00] Može is puno dalje

422
00:22:58,180 --> 00:22:59,980
[SPEAKER_00] Da nam na neki način

423
00:22:59,980 --> 00:23:02,160
[SPEAKER_00] Hoće otvoriti um

424
00:23:02,160 --> 00:23:04,799
[SPEAKER_00] Da je zbilja Božja puno dublja

425
00:23:04,799 --> 00:23:05,880
[SPEAKER_00] Nego što mi vidimo

426
00:23:05,880 --> 00:23:07,259
[SPEAKER_00] Možda jednog dana

427
00:23:07,259 --> 00:23:10,039
[SPEAKER_00] Budemo gledali sebe

428
00:23:10,039 --> 00:23:12,460
[SPEAKER_00] Prosvjetljene, preobražene

429
00:23:12,460 --> 00:23:13,240
[SPEAKER_00] U svjetlu

430
00:23:13,240 --> 00:23:15,940
[SPEAKER_00] Kakav će to zbor biti

431
00:23:15,940 --> 00:23:16,980
[SPEAKER_00] To je čudo jedno

432
00:23:16,980 --> 00:23:18,039
[SPEAKER_00] Nećete imat maske

433
00:23:18,039 --> 00:23:19,380
[SPEAKER_00] Neće vam trebat maske

434
00:23:19,380 --> 00:23:21,559
[SPEAKER_00] Biće drug čije

435
00:23:21,559 --> 00:23:23,700
[SPEAKER_00] Vidjet ćemo se takvi kakvi jesmo

436
00:23:23,700 --> 00:23:26,539
[SPEAKER_00] I bit ćemo sretni što jesmo takvi

437
00:23:26,539 --> 00:23:28,460
[SPEAKER_00] Evo dao Bog da nas

438
00:23:28,460 --> 00:23:31,619
[SPEAKER_00] Naš život dovede do preobraženog života

439
00:23:31,619 --> 00:23:32,740
[SPEAKER_00] Da vidimo i njega

440
00:23:32,740 --> 00:23:33,839
[SPEAKER_00] Lice mu lince

441
00:23:33,839 --> 00:23:35,619
[SPEAKER_00] I sebe kakve nas je on zamislio

442
00:23:35,619 --> 00:23:36,839
[SPEAKER_00] samislio. Amen.

